						<div class="postbody">Easiest way might be to use <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=7237" class="postlink">NES Screen Tool</a>. You can download a BMP here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=115203">https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=115203</a><!-- m --> to use as a template, so you get an indexed BMP with 4 colors (don't use more colors than that). NES Screen Tool can convert a BMP image to CHR pattern data for you, and it can also make edits if you don't have a good image editor.</div>

