						<div class="postbody">In Photoshop, you can reduce the image to 128x128 pixels (or smaller), and change color mode to 'indexed', 'custom palette', choose 4 colors...<br /><br />...some people use posterize filter to reduce to 4 colors...<br /><br />Open YY-CHR.<br /><br />Photoshop, select all, cut. Paste to YY-CHR.<br /><br /><br />Edit, nobody uses pyNES because it has no documentation or example code.</div>

					
